| All discourse within education
| Characterization, description, explanation, prediction, prescription, evaluation, justification of discourse within education,
|-
| Normative philosophical educology
| Intrinsically and extrinsically good and bad states of affairs for and within education
| Characterization, description, explanation, prediction, prescription, evaluation, justification of intrinsically and extrinsically good states of affairs for and within education
