{{Infobox school |name = Gymnasium Kadaň |native_name = |latin_name = Gymnasium Caadanense |logo = Logo Gymnázium Kadaň.jpg |seal_image = |image = Gymnázium Kadaň pano.jpg |image_size = |alt = Gymnasium Kadaň |caption = |motto = Consultum bene iuventae est |motto_translation = Youth in good hands |region = |city = [[Kadaň]] |province = [[Ústí nad Labem Region]] |county = |postalcode = 43201 |country = [[Czech Republic]] |coordinates = |schooltype = [[Gymnasium (school)|Gymnasium]] |fundingtype = |type = |religious_affiliation = |religion = |denomination = |patron = |established = 1803 |status = open |category = |category_label = |oversight = |oversight_label = |school code = |headmaster = Mgr. Tomáš Oršulák, Ph.D. |teaching_staff = 30 (2013/14) |students = 287 (2013/14) |classes = 14 |ratio = |language = [[Czech language|Czech]] |url = [http://www.gymnazium-kadan.cz// gymnazium-kadan.cz] }} '''Gymnasium Kadaň''' ({{lang-cz|Gymnázium Kadaň}}) is a Czech regional [[Gymnasium (school)|gymnasium]] in the [[Ústí nad Labem Region]] of [[Kadaň]]. '''[[Gymnasium (school)|Gymnasium]]''' is the oldest school in [[Kadaň]] and fifth oldest in [[Ústí nad Labem Region]]. The school was established in 1803 with 99 students and continued under the control of the [[Piarists]] until 1823. The institute of Gymnasium was then reestablished in 1872 in a new building. The Gymnasium was again closed in 1951 by communist education reform. A new Gymnasium was established in 1958. {{coord|50.3802894|N|13.2721725|E|display=title}}
