The '''Ministry of Education, Employment and Gender Affairs''' is a ministry of the [[Cayman Islands]]. It is headquartered on the fifth floor of the Government Administration Building in [[George Town, Cayman Islands|George Town]], [[Grand Cayman]], [[Cayman Islands]].<ref>"[http://www.education.gov.ky/portal/page/portal/mehhome/aboutus/contactus Contact Us]." Ministry of Education, Employment and Gender Affairs. Retrieved on September 15, 2016. "Physical Address 5th Floor, Government Administration Building, 133 Elgin Avenue, George Town, Grand Cayman, Cayman Islands"</ref>
The '''Cayman Islands Department of Education Services''' ('''DES''') operates public schools on the island. It is headquartered in a separate building in George Town.<ref>"[http://www.des.edu.ky/addresses.cfm Contact Info]." Department of Education Services. Retrieved on September 15, 2016. "Department of Education Services 130 Thomas Russell Avenue P.O. Box 910 Grand Cayman KY1-1103 CAYMAN ISLANDS"</ref>
